        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="#articles"
           data-google-event="lp_article_anchor_click"
           data-google-category="lp"
           data-google-label="hero_secondary_articles">
          判断前の記事を読む
        </a>
        <span class="hero-microcopy">勧誘なし・3分で登録完了・いつでも退会OK。FXの申込みを急がせるものではありません。</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">7日間</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">順番に届く<br/>教育LINE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">FX</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">メイン収益の<br/>判断軸</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">副業</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">収益の土台<br/>節税まで整理</span>
