        <div class="problem-card reveal" style="animation-delay:.2s">
          <div class="problem-num">03</div>
          <div class="problem-icon">¥¥</div>
          <div class="problem-title">FXで利益が出ても<br/>税金・確定申告が分からない</div>
          <div class="problem-body">確定申告・経費・損益通算。情報が多すぎて自分のケースに何が当てはまるか分からない。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── DECISION PATH ───────────────── -->
  <section class="section section--tint">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <div class="editorial-label">7-day Flow</div>
